description: During the Gold Rush, miners would often turn to quick meals so as to not disrupt their exhaustive search for gold. Nowadays, we can relate to those busy schedules in our own hectic lives - sometimes we even forget to eat. The Oro Food Truck is bringing sourdough, grains, bacon, and granola to make gourmet meals that will fill you up and help you get through your day, so that you can stick to your schedule without sacrificing your own health in the process. Stop by The Oro Food Truck for a meal that will power your own search for gold!
name: Oro Food Truck
